{"id":812,"slug":"when-i-wake-up-again","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/events/when-i-wake-up-again/","title":"When I Wake Up Again","company":"The Whisper Current Productions","genre":"Theatre","description":"A recording of; When I Wake Up Again is an immersive theatre piece exploring a family's journey through love, loss, and resilience. Through intimate storytelling, movement, and live music, the performance takes audiences inside the lives of a couple and their children, confronting the joys and heartbreaks that shape a life. Director and performer Sammi combines evocative voice, powerful stage presence, and symbolic elements—like water and puppetry—to create a poignant, multi-sensory experience. ★★★★½ Audiences are invited to move within the space, following the performers and engaging closely with the narrative. This is a deeply human story, where grief, love, and memory intertwine, leaving us to reflect on our own choices and connections. Please note: this event can be booked from Friday 1st May 2026 and is a pre-recorded show","duration_minutes":40,"age_suitability":"12+","image_url":"https://content.brightonfringe.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/02-09-2026-151959-4783.jpg","website":"","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/brightonfringe/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/brightonfringe","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/brightonfringefestival","accessibility_features":[],"content_warnings":["Haze/Smoke Effects","Haze","Smoke","Strobe","Loud","Violence"],"cast":[],"scraped_at":"2026-05-19T15:11:15.384632","venue":{"id":98,"slug":"brighton-fringe-streaming","name":"Brighton Fringe Streaming","address":null,"url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/venues/brighton-fringe-streaming","lat":null,"lng":null},"performances":[{"id":33784,"date":"2026-05-31","time":"","standard_price":null,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"booking_url":""},{"id":33785,"date":"2026-05-13","time":"23:59","standard_price":15.0,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"